{"tid":906623,"cid":18,"subCid":6,"title":"英國快報：NASA影倒太陽附近出現地球size既發光橙UFO","createTime":"2018-11-18T06:55:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-03T19:44:08.000Z","uid":165773,"like":30,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"842dbe69345a94e63d0f88de343f1f4f54f2c79d","tid":906623,"uid":165773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T06:55:40.000Z","msg":"2018Nov9<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.express.co.uk/news/weird/1043258/UFO-news-alien-spacecraft-NASA-ufo-sighting-borg-cube-start-trek-Scott-Waring\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.express.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fweird%2F1043258%2FUFO-news-alien-spacecraft-NASA-ufo-sighting-borg-cube-start-trek-Scott-Waring&d=6tuXhv1Op5ZcMF%2FNsQcJwKWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=206a058e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.express.co.uk/news/weird/1043258/UFO-news-alien-spacecraft-NASA-ufo-sighting-borg-cube-start-trek-Scott-Waring</a><br />\n<br />\n最近NASA既soho觀測站<br />\n影倒唔少新既不明飛行物<br />\n例如前排果個高速既一條棍UFO<br />\n(Solar and Heliospheric Observatory)<br />\n今次呢個係發橙黃光既cube<br />\n同太陽光一樣色<br />\n好正方好L大<br />\n（好似地球咁大）<br />\n仲要發光<br />\n唔似係自然野<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2FHkQei.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2FHkQei.png&h=b5ef30d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n由上月開始<br />\n個cube已經逗留左太陽附近幾星期<br />\n入下出下好似吸能量咁<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.express.co.uk/news/weird/1032253/UFO-news-NASA-alien-cube-spacecraft-evidence-ufo-proof-Scott-Waring\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.express.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fweird%2F1032253%2FUFO-news-NASA-alien-cube-spacecraft-evidence-ufo-proof-Scott-Waring&d=6tuXhv1Op5ZcMF%2FNsQcJwKWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=e188f8bf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.express.co.uk/news/weird/1032253/UFO-news-NASA-alien-cube-spacecraft-evidence-ufo-proof-Scott-Waring</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LzAZmnC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%